LMODMAIN.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
 01 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(LOW)  SKIP(ON)
 02 TYPE(DATAIN)
 03 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH)
 04 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
 05 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)
 06 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(TURQUOISE)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                            %SCROLL ===>_VSCR+
%DSN   $PDSN                                                  %FORMAT $PFORMAT
%MEMBER$PMEMBER                                               %VOLSER $PVOLSER
%
%                         LMOD
%
%
%
%
%
%
%
%
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
@PMSG3
@PMSG4
@PMSG5
)END

OSAPPEND.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD

+
+
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
@PMSG3
@PMSG4
@PMSG5
+     APPEND
+
+     To:
+
+     Output dataset:_PODSN                                       +
+
+     Unit name      _POUNIT  +     (3380, 3390, etc or esoteric)
+     VOLSER         _POVOL +
+
+
+
+    ------------%Leading Separator+------------------------
+   _PSEP1                                                                    +
+   _PSEP2                                                                    +
+   _PSEP3                                                                    +
+
+
+    ------------%Trailing Separator+-----------------------
+   _PSEP4                                                                    +
+   _PSEP5                                                                    +
+   _PSEP6                                                                    +
)INIT
)REINIT
  REFRESH(ZCMD,PODSN,POUNIT,POVOL,PMSG1,PMSG2,PMSG3,PMSG4,PMSG5)
)PROC
)END

OSOFFLD.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD

+
+
+
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
+     Offload $PDSN
+             $PMEMBER
+
+     To:
+
+     Output dataset:_PODSN                                       +
+     Output disp:   _POD+          (SHR,MOD, or NEW)
+
+     Unit name      _POUNIT  +     (3380, 3390, etc or esoteric)
+     VOLSER         _POVOL +
+     Primary size   _POPRI+        (in tracks)
+     Secondary size _POSEC+        (in tracks)
+
+     Overwrite?     _PYN+          (Yes or No)
+
+
+    ------------%Leading Separator+------------------------
+   _PSEP1
+   _PSEP2
+   _PSEP3
+
+
+    ------------%Trailing Separator+-----------------------
+   _PSEP4
+   _PSEP5
+   _PSEP6
)INIT
)REINIT
  REFRESH(ZCMD,PODSN,POD,POUNIT,POVOL,POPRI,POSEC,PYN,
          PMSG1,PMSG2,PMSG3,PMSG4,PMSG5)
)PROC
)END

OSSAVE.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
  ^ TYPE(INPUT)   INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)   JUST(ASIS)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%COMMAND ===>^ZCMD

+
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
@PMSG3
@PMSG4
@PMSG5
+
+     Save    $PDSN
+             $PMEMBER
+
+     To:
+
+     Output dataset:_PODSN                                       +
+            member :_POMEM   +
+     Output disp:   _POD+          (SHR,MOD, OLD, or NEW)
+
+     Unit name      _POUNIT  +     (3380, 3390, etc or esoteric)
+     VOLSER         _POVOL +
+     Primary size   _POPRI+        (in tracks)
+     Secondary size _POSEC+        (in tracks)
+
+
+     Overwrite?     _PYN+          (Yes or No)
+
+
+
+
+     Or Unix PATH: ^POPATH
+
+
+
+                    +
+
+
)INIT
)REINIT
  REFRESH(ZCMD,PODSN,POD,POUNIT,POVOL,POPRI,POSEC,PYN,
          PMSG1,PMSG2,PMSG3,PMSG4,PMSG5)
)PROC
)END

OSVRAW.text:
)ATTR
  | AREA(DYNAMIC) EXTEND(ON)   SCROLL(ON)
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
 01 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(LOW)  SKIP(ON)
 02 TYPE(DATAIN)
 03 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH)
 04 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(YELLOW)
 05 TYPE(DATAOUT) INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW) EXPAND(//)
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                            %SCROLL ===>_VSCR+
%
%               VTOC contents of volume @PVOLSER  (Raw)
%
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
+
|VDATA ---------------------------------/ /------------------------------------|
|                                       / /                                    |
| --------------------------------------/-/------------------------------------|
)INIT
)REINIT
  REFRESH(ZCMD,VSCR,VDATA)
)PROC
  &VVDEPTH = LVLINE(VDATA)
)END

SEPHELP.text:
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
+
+
%                  Available variables for separator(s)
+
%  &&DSN           +Data set name
%  &&MEMBER        +Member name
%  &&DATE1         +Julian date       YYDDD
%  &&DATE2         +Julian date       YY.DDD
%  &&DATE3         +Date              DDMMYYYY
%  &&DATE4         +Date              DD/MM/YYYY
%  &&DATE5         +Date              MMDDYYYY
%  &&DATE6         +Date              DD/MM/YYYY
%  &&DATE7         +Date              YYYYMMDD
%  &&DATE8         +Date              YYYY/MM/DD
%  &&SEQ           +Sequence nbr      (00001, 00002, etc.  Five digits)
%  &&TIME1         +Time              HH:MM:SS
%  &&TIME2         +Time              HH:MM:SS:th
%  &&RECORDS       +Number of records
%  &&SIZE          +Size in bytes
)END

X.text:
)PANEL
)ATTR
  @ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) COLOR(RED)  CAPS(OFF)
  + TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(LOW)
  % TYPE(TEXT)    INTENS(HIGH)
  $ TYPE(OUTPUT)  INTENS(HIGH) SKIP(ON)    JUST(ASIS)
  ^ TYPE(INPUT)   INTENS(HIGH) CAPS(OFF)   JUST(ASIS)
)BODY WIDTH(&ZSCREENW)
%=>_ZCMD
+                    On Screen
@PMSG1
@PMSG2
@PMSG3
@PMSG4
@PMSG5
+
+               For  Sequential or member
+
               %DSN: _PDSN                                       +
            %Member: _PMEMBER +

           %or   DD: _PDD     +

                                                                               +
            %VOLSER: _PVOLSER+

      %Start record: _PFIRST    +
    %Number to read: _PRECORDS  +

+
+
+
+               For  VSAM
+
               %RBA: _PRBA      +
           %FROMKEY: _PFROMK                                 +
             %TOKEY: _PTOK                                   +
+
+
+
+               For  Unix path
+
              %PATH: ^PPATH
+
+
+
+                   Format
+
            %Format: _PFORMAT +

)INIT
)REINIT
  REFRESH(ZCMD,PMSG1,PMSG2,PMSG3,PMSG4,PMSG5)
)END
